{"tid":1164974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得謝東閔嗰首得失一笑中其實係唱緊牙朗既人生？","createTime":"2019-05-21T13:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T13:19:53.000Z","uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"468e2c02d8d46417cfd69afb58b7b8a656f2417e","tid":1164974,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"特別副歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n横越這個世上殺敵無數 （英超西甲意甲通殺）被蒼天作弄（葡萄牙國家隊隊友唔掂）<br />\n每個變幻如像看通又狂傲似瘋（由曼聯過檔皇馬之後以為會踢到退役 點知肉酸雷逼走）<br />\n成就世界最大縱被崇拜得失一笑中（拎到幾次金球獎都比人質疑）<br />\n誰伴我（即係無） 攀得上巔峰 甘於兩袖清風（看透球壇世事）<br />\n<br />\n好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56e59639bc77dbd48ae3812c723cc7ec81ada13","tid":1164974,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"有無人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea3fe2facdd4bd4b2bdf861e739d6f25f993150","tid":1164974,"uid":53990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"屌，美欺咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7b49b9e2be7835a4237e1975f9ca23e6548a2","tid":1164974,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ea3fe2facdd4bd4b2bdf861e739d6f25f993150","tid":1164974,"uid":53990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"屌，美欺咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"美欺無點轉過會"}]}